 Water Crisis as Early as 2014 &amp; Lied About It to Congress</a></li><li><a data-ga-action="Widget: Headline" href="/2020/4/17/headlines/alaska_says_surgical_abortions_could_be_banned_during_coronavirus_pandemic">Alaska Says Surgical Abortions Could Be Banned During Coronavirus Pandemic</a></li></ul></div><a class="view_more visible-xs" data-ga-action="Headlines: More" href="/headlines">View All</a><a class="view_more button_red hidden-xs" data-ga-action="Headlines: More" href="/headlines">View All</a></div></div></div></div></div><div id="most_popular"><div class="container-fluid"><div class="row"><h5>Most popular</h5><ul><li class="col-lg-3 col-sm-6 col-md-6"><div class="number">1</div><div class="title"><a data-ga-action="Home Popular: Item" href="/2020/4/15/dr_armen_henderson_arrest_miami">&#8220;I Want an Apology&#8221;: Black Doctor Who Tests Homeless for Coronavirus Handcuffed by Miami Police</a></div><div class="share visible-lg-block"><a class="facebook popup" data-ga-action="Home Popular: Facebook" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://www.democracynow.org/2020/4/15/dr_armen_henderson_arrest_miami"><img src="https://assets.democracynow.org/assets/icons/facebook_icon-383f96e0838a32a73a62e1001107be558f0c3b34167b68b48b8bcd07bcb980fc.png" /></a><a class="twitter popup" data-ga-action="Home Popular: Twitter" href="https://twitter.com/share?url=https://www.democracynow.org/2020/4/15/dr_armen_henderson_arrest_miami&amp;text=%E2%80%9CI+Want+an+Apology%E2%80%9D%3A+Black+Doctor+Who+Tests+Homeless+for+Coronavirus+Handcuffed+by+Miami+Police&amp;via=democracynow&amp;lang=en"><img src="https://assets.democracynow.org/assets/icons/twitter_icon-7ada1bbfdd3f271ee243db9b8bab0a7dfa23a0b1f3083b054bc6923f776d9bdf.png" /></a></div></li><li class="col-lg-3 col-sm-6 col-md-6"><div class="number">2</div><div class="title"><a data-ga-action="Home Popular: Item" href="/2020/4/15/black_doctor_handcuffed_by_miami_cop">Black Doctor Handcuffed by Miami Cop as He Wore a Mask Is Critical of Florida&#8217;s Pandemic Response</a></div><div class="share visible-lg-block"><a class="facebook popup" data-ga-action="Home Popular: Facebook" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://www.democracynow.org/2020/4/15/black_doctor_handcuffed_by_miami_cop"><img src="https://assets.democracynow.org/assets/icons/facebook_icon-383f96e0838a32a73a62e1001107be558f0c3b34167b68b48b8bcd07bcb980fc.png" /></a><a class="twitter popup" data-ga-action="Home Popular: Twitter" href="https://twitter.com/share?url=https://www.democracynow.org/2020/4/15/black_doctor_handcuffed_by_miami_cop&amp;text=Black+Doctor+Handcuffed+by+Miami+Cop+as+He+Wore+a+Mask+Is+Critical+of+Florida%E2%80%99s+Pandemic+Response&amp;via=democracynow&amp;lang=en"><img src="https://assets.democracynow.org/assets/icons/twitter_icon-7ada1bbfdd3f271ee243db9b8bab0a7dfa23a0b1f3083b054bc6923f776d9bdf.png" /></a></div></li><li class="col-lg-3 col-sm-6 col-md-6"><div class="number">3</div><div class="title"><a data-ga-action="Home Popular: Item" href="/2020/4/10/noam_chomsky_trump_us_coronavirus_response">Noam Chomsky on Trump&#8217;s Disastrous Coronavirus Response, Bernie Sanders &amp; What Gives Him Hope</a></div><div class="share visible-lg-block"><a class="facebook popup" data-ga-action="Home Popular: Facebook" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://www.democracynow.org/2020/4/10/noam_chomsky_trump_us_coronavirus_response"><img src="https://assets.democracynow.org/assets/icons/facebook_icon-383f96e0838a32a73a62e1001107be558f0c3b34167b68b48b8bcd07bcb980fc.png" /></a><a class="twitter popup" data-ga-action="Home Popular: Twitter" href="https://twitter.com/share?url=https://www.democracynow.org/2020/4/10/noam_chomsky_trump_us_coronavirus_response&amp;text=Noam+Chomsky+on+Trump%E2%80%99s+Disastrous+Coronavirus+Response%2C+Bernie+Sanders+%26+What+Gives+Him+Hope&amp;via=democracynow&amp;lang=en"><img src="https://assets.democracynow.org/assets/icons/twitter_ico